20-5_6f70acb472d2496ba1587f8ceb8b10fe_master-100x100.webp 100w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-5_6f70acb472d2496ba1587f8ceb8b10fe_master.webp 960w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" src=\"/userfiles/image/backup/1714630624g20-5_6f70acb472d2496ba1587f8ceb8b10fe_master-360x360.webp\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Đặc điểm m&aacute;y massage cổ Xiaomi Jeeback G20 xung điện</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<li>N&acirc;ng cấp c&ocirc;ng nghệ Xung Điện EMS 3.0, giải tỏa tức thời c&aacute;c cơ căng thẳng</li>\r\n	<li>Lu&ocirc;n được hỗ trợ update phần mềm qua cơ sở dữ liệu OTA của nh&agrave; h&atilde;ng.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>M&aacute;y massage cổ Jeeback</strong> điều khiển kết nối App Mihome, cuộc sống th&ocirc;ng minh tiện &iacute;ch với kiểm so&aacute;t trực quan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img alt=\"Máy Massage Cổ Vai Gáy Xiaomi Jeeback G20\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7569\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-360x360.webp\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-360x360.webp 360w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-768x768.webp 768w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-188x188.webp 188w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-600x600.webp 600w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master-100x100.webp 100w, https://vphome24.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/g20-2_7d191d4a8e004ad09112dddf2ee03474_master.webp 960w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" src=\"/userfiles/image/ba